C:\FlexCache\FMSProxy\lib64\
are readable by all users and not tied to TunnelOps-specific ACLs.

4. Bonus – Test With Generic vs Named
Test this:

Log into M3015 using TunnelOps (if still enabled) → app works?

Log into same machine with ed.ball → app fails?

That confirms the mismatch is in per-user profile/environment setup, not RDP or network.

